tags.name: Station Parade
tags.note: An earlier mapper had asserted that this stretch of road is "not" Noel Rd. The BT phone-box and the addresses for these shops in the Royal Mail Post-code facility all show Station Parade to be on Noel Rd.

tags.name: Queens Drive
tags.note: An earlier mapper had given the name of this stretch of road as "Princes Gardens", a nearby subsidiary road to this one. London Underground, which owns the bridge asserts "Queens Drive".
